LaKeith Raqib AMIR-SHARIF, petitioner,
v.
Bryan COLLIER, Executive Director, Texas Department of Criminal Justice, et al. No. 16-6958. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 21, 2017.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for *1073writ of certiorari dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
